text:
The place or known as Dawson area went through several transformation. New high rise buildings which look like private condominiums. The buildings are situated near black and white bungalows.

These are actually new designed HDB buildings with sky gardens and playgrounds.

The colours of the building are different from common HDB building' colours.

Note this bus stop have 32, and the stop before this is after Tanglin road

Note: it does not turn into Queenstown Secondary school
